citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately 1138
on 07 July 23.
Upon arrival at the facility I rang the Ring doorbell and the home owner spoke with me through the Ring. He stated that
Mr. Mooney has not lived at this address since May 2023 and that he did not know his whereabouts. Upon returning to the
vehicle I called the contact number provided and received an automatic reply message saying that the call could not be
completed as dialed. I then left the facility.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately 1138 
on 07 July 23. 
 
Upon arrival at the facility I rang the Ring doorbell and the home owner spoke with me through the Ring. He stated that 
Mr. Mooney has not lived at this address since May 2023 and that he did not know his whereabouts. Upon returning to the 
vehicle I called the contact number provided and received an automatic reply message saying that the call could not be 
completed as dialed. I then left the facility. 
 
 
End Section
